title: Found a tv show narrated by Nasus
body: i just turned the tv on and some american show called nasa's unexplained files, i think, i didnt pay much attention because i swear it was Nasus narrating it in a very similar voice to the Azir/shurima story. so i just sat there not paying attention to the content but just listening to nasus talk about space and aliens  and stuff haha

replies.body: Whats the tv show? maybe there is youtube of it?
Pretty sure it was called 'Nasa's Unexplained files' but I'm not sure.
I was gonna say the voice actor for nasus is dead but I forgot about his VU for a moment.
